{"word":"H1254 - בָּרָא - bârâʼ - baw-raw' - Choose","slug":"H1254","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּרָא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>bârâʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>baw-raw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Choose"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05E8;&#x05D0; - ba&#x0302;ra&#x0302;'</b> - <i>baw-raw'</i><p/>A primitive root; (absolutely) to <i>create</i>; (qualified) to <i>cut</i> down (a wood), <i>select</i>, <i>feed</i> (as formative processes): - choose, create (creator), cut down, dispatch, do, make (fat)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1274\">H1274</a>, <a href=\"#/H1277\">H1277</a>"}]}